      "listItems": [
        "Abdullah Ali",
        "May 8, 2024",
        "How Integrating Microsoft Fabric with Databricks Enhances Functionality?Specific Benefits for Different Industries Include",
        "Specific Benefits for Different Industries Include",
        "Steps to Integrate Microsoft Fabric with Databricks",
